metadata.name: The way back home # 2
metadata.description:
Every year on this day, this location is filled with visitors
snapping photos of the revered cat monument.

No one knows when this statue was made. 
And what was it made for? 
The cat's face turned to something that no one knew.
Someone once said that if we make a wish in front of this monument,it will come true.

Blessings that will make people want to fall in love with you. As a result, it became a local legend.

Richy and Lucky here stopped on their way home. Suddenly, a strange girl approached Lucky and asked to take a picture with him.
Will the legend come true, or just Lucky is still Lucky in love all day long?
....
